### Test Order Service API

### Swagger UI
# Open: http://localhost:5255/swagger

### Create Order - Success Case
POST http://localhost:5255/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "test@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "productCode": "PROD-001",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productCode": "PROD-002",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Get Order by ID (replace {orderId} with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:5255/api/orders/{orderId}

### Get All Orders
GET http://localhost:5255/api/orders

### Get Orders by Customer Email
GET http://localhost:5255/api/orders?customerEmail=test@example.com

### Get Orders by Status
GET http://localhost:5255/api/orders?status=Pending

### Create Another Order
POST http://localhost:5255/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "productCode": "PROD-003",
      "quantity": 5
    }
  ]
}
